#### CHECK IDDNAS
  day-activate independent
  day-run script_mode check_iddnas --workdir /path/to/work/dir --config script_mode=yes remote-sample-sheet=xx remote-sample-id=XXXXXXX inbam=/path/to/XXXXXX.bam  rule_action='{\"ultraplex_iddnas\":\"run\"}'
  # /out/dir/ and XXXXXXX all need to be replaced. --sample-id should match bam sampleid
  # -s

###  SINGLE SAMPLE
     day-activate independent
     day-run check_iddnas --workdir /path/to/work/dir? --config day_i=yes sample-id=XXXXXXX inbam=/path/to/XXXXXX.bam odir=/out/dir/ ofq1=XXXXX1.fasta ofq2=XXXXX2.fasta


.... if you tab tab the command with no args a little more info is shared.
"""

